```catala-metadata
declaration abs_f
  content integer
  depends on x content integer
  equals
    if x > 0 then x else -x

declaration scope S:
  input i content integer
  context ic content integer
  context output oc content integer
  output sr content integer

scope S:
  definition ic equals abs_f of 10
  definition oc equals abs_f of 100
  definition sr equals i + ic + oc

#[test]
declaration scope T:
  output r content integer

scope T:
  definition r equals (output of S with { -- i: 1 }).sr

#[test]
declaration scope T2:
  output r content integer

scope T2:
  definition r equals (output of S with { -- i: 2 -- ic: abs_f of 20 -- oc: 200 }).sr
```

